== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
2017年1月，[[艾迪·墨菲|艾迪·墨菲]]構想和主演的1988年電影《[[來去美國|來去美國]]》將開發續集，{{le|凱文·米舍|Kevin Misher}}參與監製，首集編劇{{le|貝瑞·W·布勞斯坦|Barry W. Blaustein}}和{{le|大衛·謝菲爾德|David Sheffield}}回歸編寫劇本。然而，主角墨菲與{{le|阿塞尼奧·霍爾|Arsenio Hall}}尚未確定回歸參與。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/entertainment/news/coming-to-america-sequel-in-the-works-with-original-writers-w476909|title=A 'Coming to America' Sequel Is in the Works With the Original Writers|last=Falcone|first=Dana Rose|date=2017-04-14|work=Us Weekly|publisher=American Media, Inc.|access-date=2019-08-23|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919160333/https://www.usmagazine.com/entertainment/news/coming-to-america-sequel-in-the-works-with-original-writers-w476909/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年1月11日，墨菲和霍爾確認回歸的同時，{{le|克雷格·布魯爾|Craig Brewer}}簽約擔任導演；布魯爾先前曾和墨菲在[[Netflix|Netflix]]電影《[[我叫多麥特|我叫多麥特]]》（2019年）中合作。<ref name="Deadline(2019-01-11)">{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/01/coming-to-america-sequel-eddie-murphy-craig-brewer-directing-dolemite-is-my-name-1202533726/|title=Craig Brewer To Direct Eddie Murphy In 'Coming To America 2' For Paramount|last=Fleming Jr.|first=Mike|date=2019-01-11|website=Deadline Hollywood|publisher=Penske Media Corporation|access-date=2019-08-23|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107225816/https://deadline.com/2019/01/coming-to-america-sequel-eddie-murphy-craig-brewer-directing-dolemite-is-my-name-1202533726/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

