e=2019-11-14 |archive-date=2020-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701162252/https://collider.com/eddie-murphy-interview-beverly-hills-cop-4-snl/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。拍攝於2019年11月9日正式結束<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B4oEeJWA7Rp/ |title=Verified ♥️#Atlanta 🎞#C2A It's a wrap folks! My thanks to our amazing "Coming 2 America", staff and crew! EVERYBODY! From #craftservices to #CraigBrewer! 🎭You make us what we are |last=Hall |first=Arsenio |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |date=2019-11-09 |access-date=2019-11-15 |archive-date=2021-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307213634/https://www.instagram.com/accounts/login/ }}</ref>。年事已高的詹姆斯·厄爾·瓊斯沒去過現場與墨菲一起拍攝自己的場景。他的場景在後期製作中額外剪進去<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.looper.com/339016/the-truth-about-james-earl-jones-scenes-in-coming-2-america/ |title=The truth about James Earl Jones scenes in Coming 2 America |website=Looper |first=Dany |last=Roth |date=2021-02-22 |access-date=2021-03-03 |archive-date=2021-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307213628/https://www.looper.com/339016/the-truth-about-james-earl-jones-scenes-in-coming-2-america/ }}</ref>。

